The multiagent framework uses xmpp protocol as the communication protocal 
between agents. An implementation of XMPP in C++ is used instead of developing 
from the scratch. 
Amongs possibilities, we choose gloox. The full source code and install 
instruction of gloox can be downloaded from http://camaya.net/gloox/
The version is used for this version of opalcpp is 1.0
